CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 14, 1962, pg. 24, reads: "New Faces With Pirates - These are some of the new faces found among the 1962 Pittsburgh Pirates...  At right, above, is Orlando McFarlane, another tan rookie who figures prominently in Bucco futures.  No rookie figured in Tuesday's opening day, 6-0 scuttling of the Phillies, but Veale was named to start the second game.  Only very impressive rookies get early calls of that sort,"
TitMainTitle: Pittsburgh Pirates baseball player Orlando McFarlane kneeling on Forbes Field
